==Een kanaal bouwen==
# Open the ''Waterways construction'' toolbar by clicking the [[File:en/Manual/Manual html m2cc0c4cd.png]] button.<br/>[[File:nl/Manual/Bouw van waterwegen toolbar hk.png|frame|none|De waterwegen constructie toolbar]]
# Click on the ''Build canal'' button [[File:en/Manual/Build canal.png]]. Remember, you can right click on any button if you ever want a description of what it does.
# Place the cursor on any flat tile of land and then left-click to place the canal tile. You can also click and drag to place longer stretches of canal.<br/>[[File:en/Kanalen 1.png|frame|none|Een kanaal bouwen.]]

Once the canal is built, it's time to connect it to a lower level of water using locks.

